Prepare marinade: combine all ingredients except ham & rosemary in bowl, mix well. Pour marinade over ham steaks in dish, turning to coat evenly. Cover and refrigerate 1 hour. Prepare charcoal or gas grill. Place ham steaks on grill over medium heat. Grill ham steaks 3 to 5 minutes per side, turning once and brushing with extra marinade. Garnish with rosemary sprigs.